<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.7">
<l>āṟi ṉōṭoru nāṉkuṭai neṭumuṭi yarakkaṉṟaṉ ciramellām</l>
<l>vēṟu vēṟuka villatu vaḷaittava ṉēyeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>māṟil cōtiya maratakap pācaṭait tāmarai malarvārnta</l>
<l>tēṟal māntivaṇ ṭiṉṉicai muraltiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Lord] who bent the bow so that one-by-one all of the heads</l>
<l>Of the demon with six-and-four high crowns fell, grant me grace,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai where bees hum sweet melodies,</l>
<l rend="indent">sipping nectar</l>
<l>Which drips from lotus flowers with leaves</l>
<l rend="indent">[like] spotless, splendorous emeralds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
